<h2 id="org585ffdc"><span class="section-number-2">1.</span> <span class="todo TODO">TODO</span> Acorn Oxford, Abersywythe, Lancaster are destroyed</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-1">
<p>
Multiple branches were destroyed by ACORN National, although in slightly different circumstances. The Oxford one the branch wasn't actually destroyed, but all the active members quit, and it was replaced (by a single staff member?) who continued to run a zombie branch (and as far as I know, it still is a zombie branch). The Abersywythe one was deleted overnight for financial reasons. All of the branch social media sites were controlled by National and deleted. I'm not sure what happened in the Lancaster branch, because I haven't come across any statement put out by them.
</p>

<p>
<a href="resources/copy-of-acorn-oxford-demands.pdf">Oxford Demand Letter</a> (I've cut out the signatures from the document).
</p>

<p>
<a href="resources/acorn-aberystwyth.pdf">Acorn Abersywythe statement</a> (same thing is also explained in a)
</p>

<p>
<img src="images/fuzzy picture.jpg" alt="fuzzy picture.jpg" />
<img src="images/translated-from-welsh-article.jpg" alt="translated-from-welsh-article.jpg" />
</p>
</div>
